WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.697 align:middle line:90%


00:00:08.697 --> 00:00:10.280 align:middle line:84%
>>ZEUS YIAMOUYIANNIS:
The constituency

00:00:10.280 --> 00:00:12.857 align:middle line:84%
is no longer the market
itself or any fundamentals.

00:00:12.857 --> 00:00:14.690 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA MEREDITH: It
has no bearings, yeah.

00:00:14.690 --> 00:00:16.773 align:middle line:84%
>>YIAMOUYIANNIS: It's the
wealthiest in the world.

00:00:16.773 --> 00:00:19.190 align:middle line:84%
And so that is what's really
calling the shots now.

00:00:19.190 --> 00:00:22.460 align:middle line:84%
So there's a problem with
integrity and viability

00:00:22.460 --> 00:00:26.270 align:middle line:84%
for the generations to come
while you're serving yourself.

00:00:26.270 --> 00:00:28.610 align:middle line:84%
We have to be able to get
beyond that mentality,

00:00:28.610 --> 00:00:32.270 align:middle line:84%
but for the most part, if we
have a decent relationship,

00:00:32.270 --> 00:00:34.370 align:middle line:84%
we like it when
somebody is helping us,

00:00:34.370 --> 00:00:36.440 align:middle line:84%
and we like to
help somebody else.

00:00:36.440 --> 00:00:39.120 align:middle line:84%
We have an economy that's
doing the opposite.

00:00:39.120 --> 00:00:41.000 align:middle line:84%
We can't buy into
that programming

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:42.200 align:middle line:90%
at the metaphysical level.

00:00:42.200 --> 00:00:44.930 align:middle line:84%
We have to make our
stand, and that's

00:00:44.930 --> 00:00:46.040 align:middle line:90%
what we need to focus on.

00:00:46.040 --> 00:00:47.780 align:middle line:84%
How can we bring that
pragmatism together

00:00:47.780 --> 00:00:51.230 align:middle line:84%
with that much more fulfilling
cosmically-oriented big

00:00:51.230 --> 00:00:52.040 align:middle line:90%
everything?

00:00:52.040 --> 00:00:55.310 align:middle line:84%
And then pull our energy
away from that very low level

00:00:55.310 --> 00:00:57.900 align:middle line:84%
global sort of elite
big everything.

00:00:57.900 --> 00:00:59.570 align:middle line:90%
And we do it through the local.

00:00:59.570 --> 00:01:01.070 align:middle line:90%
We do it through relationships.

00:01:01.070 --> 00:01:04.685 align:middle line:84%
That heart-based feeling
is what is important.

00:01:04.685 --> 00:01:07.435 align:middle line:90%
