00:01:07.435 --> 00:01:12.740 align:middle line:90%


00:01:12.740 --> 00:01:15.620 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: In Zeus
Yiamouyiannis's 2013 book

00:01:15.620 --> 00:01:17.780 align:middle line:10%
"Transforming
Economy" he said we

00:01:17.780 --> 00:01:19.970 align:middle line:10%
were entering a
time of lawlessness

00:01:19.970 --> 00:01:21.470 align:middle line:10%
in our economic structures.

00:01:21.470 --> 00:01:23.210 align:middle line:10%
This means that the
fundamentals we'd

00:01:23.210 --> 00:01:26.660 align:middle line:10%
been investing by for decades
would no longer apply.

00:01:26.660 --> 00:01:28.110 align:middle line:90%
Well, this has come to pass.

00:01:28.110 --> 00:01:31.190 align:middle line:84%
So what does apply
in today's post-COVID

00:01:31.190 --> 00:01:33.650 align:middle line:84%
and some would say
ravaged economy?

00:01:33.650 --> 00:01:35.660 align:middle line:84%
You look at some
mainstream outlets,

00:01:35.660 --> 00:01:37.010 align:middle line:90%
oh, everything's looking good.

00:01:37.010 --> 00:01:39.880 align:middle line:84%
You go to the store, whoa, what
happened to all the products?

00:01:39.880 --> 00:01:44.090 align:middle line:84%
So there is a huge
disconnect in terms

00:01:44.090 --> 00:01:45.980 align:middle line:84%
of what we're
witnessing on the ground

00:01:45.980 --> 00:01:48.050 align:middle line:84%
and seeing among
people compared to what

00:01:48.050 --> 00:01:50.810 align:middle line:90%
they're reporting on MSNBC.

00:01:50.810 --> 00:01:51.830 align:middle line:90%
>>YIAMOUYIANNIS: Right.

00:01:51.830 --> 00:01:53.660 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And can I
read something, Zeus,

00:01:53.660 --> 00:01:55.910 align:middle line:84%
