00:02:12.045 --> 00:02:13.670 align:middle line:84%
I don't think there's
a person watching

00:02:13.670 --> 00:02:15.200 align:middle line:90%
this that doesn't get that.

00:02:15.200 --> 00:02:18.170 align:middle line:84%
So go ahead and open it
up with your comments

00:02:18.170 --> 00:02:20.510 align:middle line:84%
