revenues were going down,

00:02:35.900 --> 00:02:38.482 align:middle line:84%
the market itself was
going up, and that can--

00:02:38.482 --> 00:02:39.440 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: That's wrong.

00:02:39.440 --> 00:02:40.370 align:middle line:90%
>>YIAMOUYIANNIS: That was wrong.

00:02:40.370 --> 00:02:42.320 align:middle line:84%
We knew that something
was wrong there.

