and to subsidize billionaires.

00:16:46.590 --> 00:16:48.200 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:16:48.200 --> 00:16:51.500 align:middle line:84%
OK, and then just to get
us even more riled up--

00:16:51.500 --> 00:16:53.720 align:middle line:90%
[laughter]

