talking about, oh my god, they

00:17:03.510 --> 00:17:04.310 align:middle line:90%
have to--

00:17:04.310 --> 00:17:07.609 align:middle line:84%
Tower Cafe, and they
have to open back up.

00:17:07.609 --> 00:17:09.319 align:middle line:84%
That's the heartbeat
of this city,

00:17:09.319 --> 00:17:12.950 align:middle line:84%
and I think many, many people
in the city of Sacramento

00:17:12.950 --> 00:17:16.650 align:middle line:84%
would argue, this is the
heartbeat of Sacramento.

00:17:16.650 --> 00:17:18.800 align:middle line:84%
So they got through that
first period of time.

00:17:18.800 --> 00:17:22.430 align:middle line:84%
They had to close for a
while, and Jim, the owner,

00:17:22.430 --> 00:17:24.263 align:middle line:84%
