00:17:24.263 --> 00:17:26.305 align:middle line:84%
>>YIAMOUYIANNIS: The
Paycheck Protection Program.

00:17:26.305 --> 00:17:28.040 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Protection
Program, PPP.

00:17:28.040 --> 00:17:31.460 align:middle line:84%
He was working with them,
had all his financials out.

00:17:31.460 --> 00:17:35.030 align:middle line:84%
And this is a large cafe,
does a lot of business.

00:17:35.030 --> 00:17:38.180 align:middle line:84%
And he was OKed
by the government

00:17:38.180 --> 00:17:42.260 align:middle line:84%
to get the PPP loan
of up to $2 million

00:17:42.260 --> 00:17:45.717 align:middle line:84%
to pump back in for
