It's a general strike of about
12 million people saying,

00:22:22.930 --> 00:22:24.820 align:middle line:84%
I don't want or
need this anymore.

00:22:24.820 --> 00:22:25.720 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: I don't want to
live like that anymore.

00:22:25.720 --> 00:22:26.890 align:middle line:84%
>>YIAMOUYIANNIS: I don't
want to live like that.

00:22:26.890 --> 00:22:29.370 align:middle line:84%
